column1: # Migration Test Dataset for FigRegistry-Kedro Plugin
# This dataset supports migration scenario testing from manual figure management to automated plugin integration
# Contains legacy data patterns that historically required manual plt.savefig() calls and styling decisions
# Enables validation that automated plugin behavior matches previous manual workflows
# Designed to test backward compatibility and robustness during migration scenarios
# - experiment_id: Unique identifier for experimental runs
# - condition: Primary experimental condition that would trigger different styling rules
# - timepoint: Temporal dimension for baseline/followup analysis
# - treatment_group: Treatment vs control grouping for comparative analysis
# - model_type: Model comparison scenarios for algorithm evaluation
# - significance_level: Statistical significance indicators for result visualization
# - metric_value: Primary measurement value for plotting
# - secondary_metric: Additional measurement for multi-dimensional analysis
# - error_margin: Error bars or confidence intervals
# - sample_size: Number of observations for statistical validation
# - outlier_flag: Identifies data points that would need special handling
# - legacy_filename: Historical naming patterns that manual workflows would have used
# - manual_style_notes: Comments indicating what manual styling decisions would have been made
